      • checkJstZNodeWaitIfNeeded

        public static boolean checkJstZNodeWaitIfNeeded(CuratorFramework client,
                                                java.lang.String rootPath,
                                                java.lang.String jobID,
                                                long jsTime)
                                         throws Twister2Exception
        Job master creates job submission time znode under job znode, as the last action to create job related znodes at ZK server workers wait for the job master to create this znode. They proceed after seeing that this jst znode is created

        this jst znode may exist from previous runs in the case of restarting from a checkpoint because of this, its value has to be compared

        Throws:
        Twister2Exception
